casebody.data:
John PAFF, Plaintiff-Petitioner,
v.
TOWNSHIP OF MOORESTOWN and Patricia L. Hunt in Her Capacity as Records Custodian for the Township of Moorestown, Defendants-Respondents. C-443 September Term 2018
081696 Supreme Court of New Jersey. January 11, 2019

ORDER

A petition for certification of the judgment in A-005001-16 having been submitted to this Court, and the Court having considered the same;

It is ORDERED that the petition for certification is denied, with costs.
